data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN @ 5.125% INTEREST RATE! - Have you been waiting for a gorgeous home close to Mainstreet where you don't have to worry about upgrades and updates for under $550,000? Wait no more and welcome to "The Luxe on Latigo"! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has everything you've been waiting for including: natural sunlight beams off of the new laminate hardwood floors, there is fresh interior & exterior paint, new trim, new light fixtures & ceiling fans, brand new roof & gutters (October 2023!), new outlets with USB plug-ins, new light switches, and a full kitchen update that includes: new stainless steel appliances, freshly painted cabinets, refinished countertops and a brand new backsplash. The furnace and A/C have both been serviced in 2023. You're close to shopping and less than 1 mile from Mainstreet. The fence has been freshly stained and the trees have been freshly trimmed making the big, private backyard a dream. The unfinished basement with a rough-in bathroom adds opportunity for future growth, too! "The Luxe on Latigo" is everything you've been waiting for. WELCOME HOME! All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyers and Buyers Agent responsible for verifying all info. Sellers have 2 dogs and a young child so minimum 2 hours required for all showings. VA loan is only assumable for VA borrowers.
